==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Џ''', '''џ''' (''italics: Џ, џ'')

#The twenty-seventh letter of the Serbian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''џ''' (dž) and it has a similar sound to the English '''dg''' in ''do'''dg'''e''. It is preceded by [[ч|Ч]] and followed by [[ш|Ш]].

